Ice Cold Sandwich
HTC Glacier
======================================

To get started with Android, you'll need to get familiar with [Git and Repo] (http://source.android.com/download/using-repo).

To initialize repository run this command:

repo init -u git://github.com/firesnatch/icecold_android.git


Then to sync up:

    repo sync


To build:

    . build/envsetup.sh

    lunch full_glacier-userdebug

    device/htc/glacier/extract-files.sh

    make -j4 otapackage
